{{Top|leg|title=''Martial''-class shuttle}}
The '''''Martial''-class shuttle''' was a [[Starship/Legends|starship]] used in boarding operations. Produced by [[Sienar Fleet Systems/Legends|Sienar Fleet Systems]], the ship was small enough that three could fit into a retrofitted landing bay in a [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvette]]. They were in use since at least [[5 ABY/Legends|5 ABY]].

